        <note>The manuscript was sold in 1692/1693 for the price of 1000 akçe. On folio 3r we find Boris Kokenaj’s signature in Arabic script. Located in the margins throughout the manuscript we find linguistic remarks written in pencil by Józef Sulimowicz
